      <title>Docker Build Cloud setup</title>
      <link>https://docker.qubitpi.org/build-cloud/setup/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://docker.qubitpi.org/build-cloud/setup/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Before you can start using Docker Build Cloud, you must add the builder to your local&#xA;environment.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34; scroll-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;prerequisites&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;text-black dark:text-white no-underline hover:underline&#34; href=&#34;#prerequisites&#34;&gt;&#xA;    Prerequisites&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To get started with Docker Build Cloud, you need to:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Download and install Docker Desktop version 4.26.0 or later.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Sign up for a Docker Build Cloud subscription in the &#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://app.docker.com/build/&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Docker Build Cloud Dashboard&lt;span class=&#34;pl-1 icon-svg icon-sm&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;48&#34; height=&#34;48&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 -960 960 960&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M180-120q-24 0-42-18t-18-42v-600q0-24 18-42t42-18h249q12.75 0 21.38 8.68 8.62 8.67 8.62 21.5 0 12.82-8.62 21.32-8.63 8.5-21.38 8.5H180v600h600v-249q0-12.75 8.68-21.38 8.67-8.62 21.5-8.62 12.82 0 21.32 8.62 8.5 8.63 8.5 21.38v249q0 24-18 42t-42 18H180Zm600-617L403-360q-9 9-21 8.5t-21-9.5q-9-9-9-21t9-21l377-377H549q-12.75 0-21.37-8.68-8.63-8.67-8.63-21.5 0-12.82 8.63-21.32 8.62-8.5 21.37-8.5h261q12.75 0 21.38 8.62Q840-822.75 840-810v261q0 12.75-8.68 21.37-8.67 8.63-21.5 8.63-12.82 0-21.32-8.63-8.5-8.62-8.5-21.37v-188Z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34; scroll-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;use-docker-build-cloud-without-docker-desktop&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;text-black dark:text-white no-underline hover:underline&#34; href=&#34;#use-docker-build-cloud-without-docker-desktop&#34;&gt;&#xA;    Use Docker Build Cloud without Docker Desktop&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To use Docker Build Cloud without Docker Desktop, you must download and install&#xA;a version of Buildx with support for Docker Build Cloud (the &lt;code&gt;cloud&lt;/code&gt; driver).&#xA;You can find compatible Buildx binaries on the releases page of&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://github.com/docker/buildx-desktop&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;this repository&lt;span class=&#34;pl-1 icon-svg icon-sm&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;48&#34; height=&#34;48&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 -960 960 960&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M180-120q-24 0-42-18t-18-42v-600q0-24 18-42t42-18h249q12.75 0 21.38 8.68 8.62 8.67 8.62 21.5 0 12.82-8.62 21.32-8.63 8.5-21.38 8.5H180v600h600v-249q0-12.75 8.68-21.38 8.67-8.62 21.5-8.62 12.82 0 21.32 8.62 8.5 8.63 8.5 21.38v249q0 24-18 42t-42 18H180Zm600-617L403-360q-9 9-21 8.5t-21-9.5q-9-9-9-21t9-21l377-377H549q-12.75 0-21.37-8.68-8.63-8.67-8.63-21.5 0-12.82 8.63-21.32 8.62-8.5 21.37-8.5h261q12.75 0 21.38 8.62Q840-822.75 840-810v261q0 12.75-8.68 21.37-8.67 8.63-21.5 8.63-12.82 0-21.32-8.63-8.5-8.62-8.5-21.37v-188Z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
